<br>
3. Forums, we agree what forums we will have here as a community, those will be the only forums we have, addtional forums would be agreed to by the Guild Reps.  (General, FC, Guild Rep, RTA Rotations, Rules, and Elemental)  other forums as we decide/agree to them <br>
<br>
