<br>
6. Forum Moderators - People who police certain forums, their job would be lock/delete posts as necessary,  verify rules are being followed, and report any infractions to a Forum Admin <br>
<br>
7. Forum Admin would verify the offense and carry out the Admin task necessary for it.  Mainly marking a player banned.<br>
<br>
8. Rotation Managers - Theri job to work with Guilds on creating rules for new rotations, posting the rules, Adding guilds to rotations, and maintaining the database. <br>
<br>
9. Clear Cut rules for Voting in new Moderators, Admin or Managers.  We need to decide what we want them to be. Such things that come to mind ( no guild can have more than 1 person in any speicifc spot, or a guild can have no more than 3 people total)<br>
<br>
10. Regular Votes of Confidence, for the moderators, Admin, &amp; managers.  It shows the Guild Reps are backing these individuals or not,  if not then need to bring in a new person for that spot.<br>
